{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monochrome Painter tells the story of a colorless character living in a colorless world, but one day, they discovered they had the power to bring color to their world and embarked on a journey to find the colors of their realm.<br><br>This is an 8-bit-style platformer where the goal is to paint the game's environment by collecting paint buckets scattered throughout the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each collected paint bucket adds a new color to the game, and once you finish the game by gathering all the buckets, you can restart it with the environments already colored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features simple mechanics with precision jumping, monsters, and secret passages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can play using either a keyboard or a game controller. If you're using a keyboard, the character moves with the arrow keys, and jumps are performed with the &quot;X&quot; or &quot;Space&quot; keys.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game allows for the creation of additional levels, which can either replace or complement the existing levels in the game. To do this, check the files in the &quot;levels&quot; folder.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Game Over","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3258960/bcf0d22af9b109c6c93e883b35385a539312e171.jpg"},{"name":"Paint the world","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3258960/08ff224b0def6cbcf7db0f33db2f5342b8f7159f.jpg"},{"name":"Geting all lifes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3258960/a70d3501c22aa000c711ab4c005ce8494efc9072.jpg"},{"name":"Hard Level","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3258960/48b8f34c6b43fc4d939b2c1d185d87a3fc42a1db.jpg"},{"name":"Jumping in monst